01:51.077 --> 01:52.700
Alison Tisdale--

01:52.879 --> 01:55.490
24, grad student at N.Y.U.,

01:55.490 --> 01:57.238
Part of the social work program.

01:57.273 --> 01:58.899
Nice place for a social worker.

01:58.899 --> 02:00.203
Daddy's money.

02:00.294 --> 02:02.194
Neighbors called to
